Happy with all the💝 received from family and friends 🥰🤗 Food to last me the whole day and maybe days 😜
Everything I am eating today were neither prepared nor cooked by me. Isabella was saying this when she handed me the Latte :”Today u happy Lor just sit there and eat “ hahah! 
Hope your day has been great too and have a wonderful celebration day to all mummies out there ♥️💐 #happymothersday 
#StayHomeWithAscott #stayhomeforsg #SGunited #circuitbreakersg #stayhomesg

Happy Mother’s Day Mary 🌹You look damn pretty!!
@jmeteo Thank you Idol ♥️ you are always beautiful in my eyes too! Happy Mother’s Day to you 💝💐
Korean celebrity eating! You look gorgeous! Blessed Mother’s Day! 💜🌸
@kev_3es Thank you ! You are beautiful and wonderful mum yourself too ♥️😍
@cindy.thamcp thank you 🤗You too! And a wonderful mummy ♥️
@tracy_xxh you are too !!! Happy Mother’s Day to you ♥️🤗
Hope you like our flowers and have a blessed Mother’s Day!!!❤

Just a note below to share on how to keep our flowers fresh with lasting beauty. *DAILY FLOWER CARE & HANDLING
- Place our floral arrangement in a cool and ventilated place away from direct sunlight.
- Drip in moderate water to the green sponge at the bottom of our flowers to keep it moist.
- Spray some water on the flowers and foliage to keep them refreshed.
